title: mondaysRmurder EP 3: The Mystery of Stacey Stites
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: UPDATE: Jimmy Fennell will be released tomorrow from Texas prison, six months early (March 9th, 2018). Currently, Rodney Reed is still in prison.
Have you ever thought to do a voice over? I normally drive to your videos. Luckily I was already at my job today but just a suggestion. Thank you for everything you do!!

I am really enjoying this series. I have never been much of a true crime aficionado, but since my trip to Boston, that all changed. During a ghost tour and cemetery tour, our guide related to us the details about the infamous Boston Strangler. Throughout his story, all I kept thinking was, "This is so fascinating, and Ryan needs to include this in AHS! Why hasn't he done anything with Boston yet?" I am almost certain, with that intelligent devious mind of yours, you have already worked on a video about him, or have considered him a possible subject for this series. Great job!
Rodney Reed is up for execution, yikes... c’mon Texas give that man a reprieve!
